data.description: Horse Property in the trees!  Secluded, yet minutes from town with a fabulous view of the Sleeping Giant.  This home is located in the popular South Hills area overlooking the city of Helena.  There is over 5000 finished sq. feet with 6 bedrooms and 5 bathrooms spread over three levels with storage/flex space galore and two exits from the walkout basement!  The home boasts a second kitchen area in the basement with ample room for all of your guests.  Not only is there an oversized 2 car attached finished garage, but there is also a 32 x 40 shop to park all the toys, and it's already set up for horses with a corral, tack room, two covered stalls, hay shed, and year around automatic waterer.  There are three accesses to reach the home, shop, and horse corral.  Call Shawna Korth at 720-273-6390 or your real estate professional.
